#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
StormOS Welcome

A modern welcome + lightweight software center + post-install toolkit
for Arch-based StormOS.

Features
- Welcome / Quick Links
- System Actions
- Software Center (pacman, AUR/yay, flatpak, snap, appimage)
- Maintenance (cache, orphans, mirrors, keys)
- Drivers (NVIDIA, AMD, Intel, Printer, VM)
- Tweaks (services, shell, fonts, Plymouth)
- Gaming (Steam, Lutris, Proton, MangoHud, etc.)
- Settings / Appearance
- Help

Fixes vs original
- Calamares now launches in forced dark/Fusion mode
- App auto-removes its own autostart entry after StormOS is fully installed
  (detected by absence of live-session markers)
"""

